data.description:
Welcome to 20 Calico and live your best life here in the lowcountry! 3 Bedrooms / 2 Bath home that was renovated in 2022 including a new roof! Open floor concept with luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout this home. Stunning tiled bathrooms to immaculate granite counter tops in the kitchen. Great location on a quiet street. Large backyard with gorgeous trees and plenty of space for outdoor activities. NO POA/NO HOA    Minutes to MCAS & Parris Island
 Schools close by Battery Creek High, Bridges Preparatory, Low Country Montessori
